  <body>
    <div style="width:100%; ">
    <h3>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</h3>
  
    <p>On behalf of the entire  Team, we'd like to take this opportunity to welcome you as a new “Sophia Concept” member.</p>
  
    <p>Please verify the below submitted details:</p>

    <table style="width:400px; margin:50px auto 10px auto;  background:#f5f5f5; padding:1.5%; border:1px solid #cccccc;">
 
      <tbody>

        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;">First Name</td> <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;"><%= @user.first_name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr> 
         <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;">Last Name</td>  <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;"><%= @user.last_name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;">Email</td> <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;"><%= @user.email %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
         <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;">Country</td> <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;"><%= @country.country_name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;">City</td> <td style="padding: 12px;    vertical-align: top;"><%= @city.city_name %></td>
        </tr>
         
      </tbody>

  </table>
 
 <p align="center" style="font-size: 9px">For queries you can contact to our 24*7 Support team.</p>     
 
 <p> We are thrilled to have you with us. </p>
 
